flowchart LR
    %% Immutable core
    CORE[Intent core\nimmutable after create]
    CORE --> intent_id
    CORE --> intent_type
    CORE --> agents[from_agent / to_agent]
    CORE --> payload[payload: free JSON]

    %% Mutable policy
    POLICY[workflow_control_policy\nmutable]
    POLICY --> grants   --> g1[delegate:agent://ops\nallow = resume, update_controls, update_policy]
    POLICY --> controls --> c1[timeout_seconds]
    POLICY --> envelope --> e1[max_retry_count]
                envelope --> e2[retry_backoff_seconds]
                envelope --> e3[execution_timeout_seconds]
                envelope --> e4[ttl_seconds]
                envelope --> e5[expires_at]

    %% CAS mutation flow
    EP1[POST /intents/{id}/controls]
    EP2[POST /intents/{id}/policy]
    GEN[policy_generation]
    EXP[expected_policy_generation\nsent by caller]
    CAS{generation matches?}
    OK[atomic update\ngeneration++]
    ERR[409 conflict\nstale writer]

    EP1 & EP2 --> EXP
    EXP & GEN --> CAS
    CAS -->|yes| OK --> POLICY
    CAS -->|no|  ERR
